rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0001
rows.name:
This place feels so good on a sunny day.
The breeze is so gentle, the sun is so warm~

rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If it weren't for the occasional shouting,
it would be perfect, you know?

rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There are people in clunky armor who are always
shouting in a rhythmic way.

rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't know what they're doing, but
it makes it hard to take a nap.
